<table border="0" cellpadding="5" width="550" cellspacing="5" height="400" >
<tr valign="top" height="400" >
<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><i><br>(Use for those who notified us)<br></i>Thank you for your speaking with me today and for notifying us of a new potential Public Liability claim.<br></span><i style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>(Use for those where we received notification)<br></i><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">We have received notification of a potential claim being made against you for <i>(insert allegations and claimant here)</i>.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>In order that we can present a claim to insurers, please could you forward me the following:</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style=""></p><ul><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Overview of events to date leading up to the claim</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Description of the damage done and cost expected as far as you know</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Description of how the damage was caused</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">The date of when the incident occurred and when the claim was made against you</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Statement from the claimant or as much detail as you can</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Explain if you know, their view of responsibility</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Confirmation of any involvement of a further party such as client</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Copies of any quote to do the work/agreement&nbsp;</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Photographs to support the damage caused if you have any</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Copies of any prior correspondence</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Any other correspondence received - if applicable that you feel would support your potential claim</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Confirmation of your VAT status</font></li></ul><p></p><p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">I attach your policy schedule and wording to assist.<br></font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Upon receipt of the above, I will send to our insurers for review. Depending on how quickly you return the information will determine the timeframe for this.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Please note should you make a Public Liability claim and this is accepted there will be a policy excess of <i>(insert Excess/delete it not applicable) </i>as per your schedule.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>I look forward to hearing from you.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>Kind regards,<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Claims Team<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>E: claims@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">T: 01242 808 740</span></p>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>